Instead of deleting this, I'm not logging on again.&nbsp; 


I'm so tired of all of you.&nbsp; If we cross paths by chance fine, but don't any of you dare call me for a fucking thing.&nbsp; 


Peace.

Do you know how bored I have to be to look up an obscure Marvel character, study said character, and then sketch them....IN PENCIL?!?!?!?!?!?&nbsp;&nbsp;


SHADING IS MY FUCKING ENEMY!






I wonder what cool kids do on weekends.

Quick update because I should actually be leaving for a&nbsp;lab.&nbsp;&nbsp;

Getting rid of truck.&nbsp;&nbsp;Either&nbsp;getting bike or bigger truck.&nbsp; That depends on how&nbsp;skilled I am at being a conman.&nbsp; ...I&nbsp;know what youre thinking.&nbsp;&nbsp;



And now ladies and gentlemen, a tapdance.&nbsp; &nbsp;

&nbsp;Bartus is here.&nbsp; This means several things.&nbsp;&nbsp;

No sleep.&nbsp;
Lots of work.
Emma the wonder dog.&nbsp;
The day after my birthday is REALLY going to hurt.
Surf trips.&nbsp;&nbsp;


I'm really anxious to try out his longboard though.&nbsp; I thas a new rocker in it that's supposed to change the way people look at wave sizes.....We're going tomorrow morning so I guess I'll see for myself.&nbsp;&nbsp;


In other news, I may be sexist.&nbsp; Hearing a female sportscaster call a football game makes me want to change the channel.&nbsp;
